{"tid":1678412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[啟德中及南]公民黨候選人梁詠欣搞眾籌，快幫拖！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:28:48.000Z","uid":159327,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"12df2f4707d51c1105f441397e8c7d835fe5d061","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"幫手捐錢同spread出去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難得蝗屋邨有深黃候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊幫手踢走建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71306802_508311553231311_5653925348232921088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQmwNjOO1zNAmOIBU-scGKpLVMey3VJxhnXuqWLISMaa0IVMbkiGGmVLVnRDkLUAvZ0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=4e4348842e65e6de90d430d661ac3627&amp;oe=5E5F2A3E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71306802_508311553231311_5653925348232921088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQmwNjOO1zNAmOIBU-scGKpLVMey3VJxhnXuqWLISMaa0IVMbkiGGmVLVnRDkLUAvZ0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D4e4348842e65e6de90d430d661ac3627%26oe%3D5E5F2A3E&h=4c39dc92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#怒籌捐款<br />\n咏欣現正開始籌集選舉經費。<br />\n作為民主派的一員，我沒有建制派龐大無窮的資源。<br />\n每一樣選舉要用嘅野，傳單、易拉架、海報、直幡，大聲公，都係我在過去一年兼職時儲落嘅錢支付。<br />\n因為資金短缺，我只有３支直幡、３張易拉架，而對手每次開站都出動旗海戰術、人海戰術，將我嘅宣傳品遮住。<br />\n政黨只能為我提供非常有限嘅支持，為咗香港可以贏呢場仗，我已經用盡積蓄。所以希望可以喺呢度籌集資金作為選舉經費，提高呢場選舉嘅勝算。<br />\n我非常需要大家的幫助，希望向大家籌募競選經費，目標為5萬元。<br />\n以下係我銀行帳號資料，因為collection 亦有一定的手續費需要收取，希望有心人最好 #直接匯款而不經平台 ，同時亦提供匯款單方便紀錄，亦可以令籌款一分一毫都用到競選上。<br />\n由於選舉開支上限是68,000，因為如果籌多過68,000，我會按照法例要求捐去根據《稅務條例》第88 條獲豁免繳稅的屬公共性質的慈善機構。<br />\n銀行戶口 Bank Account<br />\n匯豐銀行 儲蓄戶口<br />\n004-814446183292<br />\nHSBC Saving Account 004-814446183292<br />\nLeung Wing Yan<br />\n*如捐款超過1000元正，須補上全名及住址作申報。如未能提供證明，有關捐款不能作選舉用途，並需要捐出。🙇🏻&zwj;♂<br />\n我在此感謝各位支持，我定必會繼續努力，為民主派守護社區！<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/sandraleung_2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2Fsandraleung_2019%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=0723078e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/sandraleung_2019/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有義工招募<br />\nWhatsapp:<br />\n<a href=\"http://wa.me/85256003460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwa.me%2F85256003460&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=b33c7272\" target=\"_blank\">http://wa.me/85256003460</a><br />\nTelegram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sandraleung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsandraleung&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=557d9f7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sandraleung</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/梁咏欣-Sandra-Leung-414955815900219/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%92%8F%E6%AC%A3-Sandra-Leung-414955815900219%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=21490745\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/梁咏欣-Sandra-Leung-414955815900219/posts/?ref=page_internal</a>"},{"pid":"ca4018119778a748f2aca3cfe15afdf469ec56d6","tid":1678412,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=cf70b41c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=5b984864\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4Qpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=c431dc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"3cfbc11af8d7cf4f976a808db96db944421e6c7d","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c0c84f8d413614a87164483236831d5032a24541","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb4863aec7e3febf2c83744cc5b33ee014c72135","tid":1678412,"uid":176307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd0f939c9abbedb27e51f502be34c064b3c8ffe5","tid":1678412,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79c727fafbd05d5e1d304b310f42f22aa81dd939","tid":1678412,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Az48uO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Az48uO.jpg&h=5746821e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phBnU9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphBnU9O.jpg&h=18c9713b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a875c9343a97eb382dad3b339c42973750e49e10","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:00:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"50048739bf4e09cdd8880aeaca8710d2686044eb","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c1df7edad10214195fac0690d02d22bf7a3cbd8b","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1c600929c66b7d6a045f9cdff59a07ab268fc76f","tid":1678412,"uid":159327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"wish"},{"pid":"ffc580d373e4917791caff6b3d1